You shut up, you big female asshole!

4
00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:39.400 
别推我
Hey, don't shove me!

5
00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:40.520 
- 我没有 - 什么你没有
- I didn't! - You didn't what?

6
00:03:40.600 --> 00:03:41.860 
- 你什么毛病 - 你又是什么毛病
- What's your problem? - What's yours?

7
00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:43.100 
- 闭嘴 - 你才闭嘴
- Shut up! - You shut up!

8
00:03:43.660 --> 00:03:44.580 
嗷 噢
-wh-whoa, whoa!

9
00:03:44.680 --> 00:03:47.100 
搞什么鬼鬼鬼鬼鬼
What the hell, hell, hell, hell, hell?

10
00:03:47.300 --> 00:03:49.640 
你们搞什么
Oh, god. Oh, no. What did you guys just do?

11
00:03:49.700 --> 00:03:50.580 
什么意思
what do you mean?

12
00:03:49.700 --> 00:03:50.580 
你说谁
What did who do?

13
00:03:50.660 --> 00:03:51.760 
等等 我在说什么
Wait, what am I saying?

14
00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:54.420 
刚才是不是有谁有什么不确定的事儿
Were either of you guys uncertain about anything just now?

15
00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:56.500 
天 我感觉好难受
Oh, man, I don't feel good.

16
00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:57.840 
我还是我吗
Am I me?

17
00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:58.080 
我在说话吗
Am I talking right now?

18
00:03:58.100 --> 00:03:58.900 
应该是吧
I think so.

19
00:03:58.940 --> 00:04:00.080 
谁在说话
Wait, who said that?

20
00:04:00.140 --> 00:04:01.780 
你们俩听好 先别动
All right, both of you just don't move.

21
00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:04.540 
别说话 也别瞎想 我去检查检查
Don't speak, don't think. I have to check something.

